			- We changed the way how player requests VAST XML file. Previously it loaded VAST during player
			  initialization in order to avoid any further delays when starting player. This approach worked
			  incorrectly together with 3rd-party popunders, because in most cases player page would be displayed twice
			  for the same user and KVS player didn't have any chance to know this fact, so that it could avoid VAST
