			- Added new player skin in youtube style.<br/>
			- For iOS devices player now supports metadata preload, which will allow faster video start (if you enabled
			  the needed option in player settings and device supports this).<br/>
			- Text cue points can now be set up for timeline screenshots in video screenshots editor. Such cue points
			  will be highlighted on player timeline and texts will be shown together with screenshots. Excellent
			  feature to highlight video key scenes.<br/>
			- In pre-roll and post-roll advertising settings you can now enable built-in skip button and configure when
			  it will become active. Also GUI of such advertising was changed - you can now show message with
