		</li>
		<li>
			We re-thought IP limit blocking mechanism in video protection. Since we've added video file link
			obfuscation feature in 3.9.0 player, IP limit makes no much sense anymore. Now it can be switched off and
			will ease disk utilization. Also it doesn't count skipping anymore, so protection doesn't rely on how often
			user skips video. <b>ATTENTION!</b> After updating to 3.9.1 IP limit will be automatically switched off.
