			- Placing the logo as a stripe in the bottom or at the top. These do not function properly on some devices.<br/>
			- Skipping in FLV files: we no longer recommend using FLV; use MP4 instead.<br/>
			- Ads displayed on mouse over: makes no sense for mobile devices.<br/>
			- Old player JavaScript API that used certain functions with predefined names. This may result in your
			  customised player features no longer working properly. You will need to rewrite your customisation using
			  the new API. It will be described in the FAQ.<br/>
			- Integration with the teasernet network. It is about to be replaced with VAST support in future.<br/>
