			awards that have not yet been paid out.
		</li>
		<li>
			In the <b>list_members</b> (list of members) block, you can now apply filters by all custom user fields.
		</li>
		<li>
			In the <b>list_models</b> (list of models) and <b>list_content_sources</b> (list of content sources), you
			can now use sorting by screenshots. It lets you display objects with uploaded screenshots first.
		</li>
		<li>
			Bugs that have been fixed:<br/>
			- In new ffmpeg versions, SAR of the source file would not be detected correctly.<br/>
			- When deleting content purchased by a user in the admin panel, the purchase would not be reset.<br/>
			- An issue with saving import schemes could lead to saved schemes being overwritten or modified.<br/>
			- An issue in ccbill denial processing.
		</li>
	</ul>
	<h3 id="section_whats_new_3_8_4">KVS v3.8.4 [15.05.2016]</h3>
