			- Storage server check used last added content (video or album) and with CDN could return errors as the
			  content would not have been fully uploaded to CDN.<br/>
			- When vertical videos were uploaded using the new theme, the preview screenshot would not be rotated.<br/>
			- Pagination with pseudo-random sorting resulted in empty list.<br/>
			- In new embed codes, affiliate refs would not be sent to video page.<br/>
			- In import feeds, when premium videos were imported, format was not taken into account when selected.<br/>
			- In import feeds, setting server time for imported video would work slightly incorrectly.<br/>
			- In <b>list_videos</b>, when external search plugin was used, <b>show_xxx_info</b> options would not
