			functionality of site and admin panel; by default it is disabled. If enabled, you will be able to configure
			days offset for every video and album: positive offset means that this content will become visible on N-th
			day after registration (for example <b>1</b> means that content will become visible immediately after
			registration, <b>10</b> means that content will become visible on 10th day after registration). Negative
			offset is also allowed and means that (a) this content will be visible all the time, even if user is not
			registered / logged in, (b) its publishing date will always be shifted according to the current date. For
			example relative publishing date <b>-10</b> means that content will appear to be added 10 days ago,
