	<ul>
		<li>
			In some website blocks the feature was added to display a tree structure of videos: by categories, models
			and content sources. Thus, for example, you can display a list of content sources and show N videos with
			desired sorting for each content source (rated by popularity, by rotator, etc.). Similarly, you can do for
