	<h3 id="section_whats_new_2_2_0">KVS v2.2.0 [24.03.2011]</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>
			Beta-version of rotator: the feature, which everyone had been waiting for long, was finally done! In
			version 2.2.0 we made video rotator only, but potentially in the future we have no problem to add a rotator
			for photo albums, content sources, models and DVDs. Video rotator works on 2 levels: at first level, the
			screenshots are rotated within one video to identify the most clickable(s). You can automatically remove N
			of screenshots with worst CTR. At second level, the rotation is active on all videos to identify the most
			clickable videos among others. Details of the rotator will be available in the documentation for future
			versions. So far as the feature is serious and affects the very heart of the website engine, it is locked
