			of a fixed size. In this case, depending on video ratio, the black bars may appear that may be undesirable.
		</li>
		<li>
			2 extra custom fields were added to category object.
		</li>
		<li>
			Few small corrections and bugs.
		</li>
	</ul>
	<h2 id="section_whats_new_2_1">KVS v2.1</h2>
